title: Chris Woakes puts Tests over T20s in event of concurrent England matches
description: Fast bowler itching to get back to action, even if it has to be behind closed doors | ESPNcricinfo.com
content: Chris Woakes says that England's cricketers would be open to playing behind closed doors in a bid to get the international game back up and running after the Covid-19 outbreak, but concedes that his own focus would have to be on the Test and ODI squads over T… [+6380 chars]
